OL,3,COver 100 MPs demand law change so
OL,4,Cparents of critically ill children get
OL,5,Csupport
OL,7,FOver 150 MPs and peers are urging Keir
OL,8,FStarmer to bring in a new law which
OL,9,Fwould give financial support to the
OL,10,Fparents of critically ill children,
OL,11,Fafter a campaign by a dad who lost his
OL,12,Fsix-year-old son to cancer.
OL,14,FCeri Menai-Davis walked 100km from
OL,15,FAddenbrooke's Hospital in Cambridge to
OL,16,F10 Downing Street in Westminster, to
OL,17,Fdeliver the prime minister a letter,
OL,18,Fpleading with him to give statutory
OL,19,Frights to the parents of poorly
OL,20,Fchildren.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
