OL,3,COver 100 MPs demand law change so
OL,4,Cparents of critically ill children get
OL,5,Csupport
OL,7,FAlong with wife Frances, he's been
OL,8,Fcampaigning for Hugh's Law, which
OL,9,Fwould give paid leave and job
OL,10,Fprotection to parents whose child is
OL,11,Fdiagnosed with a critical or terminal
OL,12,Fillness, up to the age of 16.
OL,14,FThe letter - signed by 153
OL,15,Fparliamentarians, including 77 from
OL,16,Fthe governing Labour Party - says "too
OL,17,Fmany parents, already facing the
OL,18,Fanguish of caring for a seriously ill
OL,19,Fchild, also face the devastating
OL,20,Freality that they cannot afford to be
OL,21,Fat their child's bedside".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
