OL,3,COver 100 MPs demand law change so
OL,4,Cparents of critically ill children get
OL,5,Csupport
OL,7,FIt adds: "Hugh's Law would introduce
OL,8,Fan immediate, non-means tested benefit
OL,9,Ffor parents of seriously ill children,
OL,10,Foffering immediate support that
OL,11,Fcurrent benefits simply do not
OL,12,Fprovide. Families must not fall
OL,13,Fthrough the cracks of the welfare
OL,14,Fsystem at what is, for many, the
OL,15,Fhardest period of their lives."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
