OL,5,Csupport
OL,7,FThe government has already confirmed
OL,8,Fit will launch a consultation into
OL,9,Fcalls for Hugh's Law in 2026, and the
OL,10,Fletter urges ministers to "announce an
OL,11,Fintention to legislate on Hugh's Law
OL,12,Fin next year's King's Speech".
OL,14,FUnder current law, parents of newborn
OL,15,Fbabies who become unwell within the
OL,16,Ffirst 28 days of life are entitled to
OL,17,Fpaid leave and job protection to be by
OL,18,Ftheir child's bedside.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
