OL,3,COver 100 MPs demand law change so
OL,4,Cparents of critically ill children get
OL,5,Csupport
OL,7,FHowever, if their child is diagnosed
OL,8,Fwith cancer at 29 days old, the
OL,9,Fparents no longer have the right to
OL,10,Ffinancial support.
OL,12,FAt present, parents of critically ill
OL,13,Fchildren must rely on unpaid Carer's
OL,14,FLeave, which is capped at just one
OL,15,Fweek per year.
OL,17,FDisability Living Allowance is
OL,18,Favailable to claim on behalf of the
OL,19,Fchild, but parents must wait 90 days
OL,20,Fbefore applying and an application can
OL,21,Ftake up to 20 weeks to be processed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
