OL,7,FCeri walked the huge distance from
OL,8,FAddenbrooke's, where his son was
OL,9,Ftreated, with the weight of Hugh -
OL,10,F20kg - in his backpack to deliver the
OL,11,Fletter which has been signed by 105
OL,12,FMPs and 48 peers.
OL,14,F"Our journey to Downing Street has
OL,15,Fbeen one of battles and fighting to
OL,16,Fget Hugh's Law to be heard. And this
OL,17,Fjourney was about that, traveling with
OL,18,Fhis weight on our back as the weight
OL,19,Fof grief and also trying to inspire
OL,20,Fparents across the country.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
