OL,5,Csupport
OL,7,F"And we realised at that point there
OL,8,Fis nothing in place in the UK that
OL,9,Fprovides support, financial support to
OL,10,Fparents of a sick child."
OL,12,FThey are urging the government to
OL,13,Fbring in support of #187 per week,
OL,14,Fwhich is significantly less than the
OL,15,Fminimum wage in the UK.
OL,17,F"Even though it's a small amount of
OL,18,Fmoney," Ceri told ITV News, "but what
OL,19,Fit does, it keeps the wheels ticking
OL,20,Fover."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
