OL,7,F"It keeps the bills being paid, keeps
OL,8,Ffood on your table. And we're just
OL,9,Fasking that the government have some
OL,10,Fempathy towards us parents."
OL,12,FHe added: "You're not only dealing
OL,13,Fwith financial trouble, you're dealing
OL,14,Fwith the fact that your child may
OL,15,Fnever come out of hospital again.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
