OL,7,F"And if you can lift the burden, the
OL,8,Ffinancial burden on these parents, and
OL,9,Fyour aim is to help the working class,
OL,10,Fthen there's no better people to help
OL,11,Fthan those who've been left behind in
OL,12,Fhospital wards."
